CustomField.description: The date used to calculate a project's variance values. The date last week that corresponds to the last day in the project's work calendar is used. If no work calendar exists, last Sunday's date is used.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The date used to calculate a project's variance values. The date last week that corresponds to the last day in the project's work calendar is used. If no work calendar exists, last Sunday's date is used.
CustomField.label: Hours Cut Off Date
